ml#Lean.Parser.Tactic.tacticLet'_","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L411-L411","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.inductionAlt","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/2879377407752611243.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.inductionAlt","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L412-L412","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.inductionAlts","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/2380395907437552519.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.inductionAlts","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L413-L413","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.induction","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/5069327674316859865.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.induction","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L415-L415","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.generalizeArg","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/12275713363721179263.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.generalizeArg","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L416-L419","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.generalize","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/6653091198570054015.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.generalize","doc":"`generalize ([h :] e = x),+` replaces all occurrences `e`s in the main goal with a fresh hypothesis `x`s.\nIf `h` is given, `h : e = x` is introduced as well. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L421-L421","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.casesTarget","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/16675780732658232935.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.casesTarget","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L422-L422","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.cases","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/6241084935010701159.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.cases","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L424-L424","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.existsIntro","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/4661644672891284933.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.existsIntro","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L426-L427","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.renameI","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/828759459020954065.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.renameI","doc":"`rename_i x_1 ... x_n` renames the last `n` inaccessible names using the given names. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L429-L429","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.tacticRepeat_","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/3072633779721027895.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.tacticRepeat_","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L433-L433","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.tacticTrivial","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/158243492662253515.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.tacticTrivial","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L435-L435","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.split","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/16218723192580453945.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.split","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L437-L443","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.specialize","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/11494927290347710701.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.specialize","doc":"The tactic `specialize h a₁ ... aₙ` works on local hypothesis `h`.\nThe premises of this hypothesis, either universal quantifications or non-dependent implications,\nare instantiated by concrete terms coming either from arguments `a₁` ... `aₙ`.\nThe tactic adds a new hypothesis with the same name `h := h a₁ ... aₙ` and tries to clear the previous one.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L451-L451","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.tacticUnhygienic_","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/2869729097448656875.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.tacticUnhygienic_","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L453-L453","name":"Lean.Parser.Tactic.fail","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/422014296507218463.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Tactic.fail","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L459-L459","name":"Lean.Parser.Attr.simp","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/1282294142236588413.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#Lean.Parser.Attr.simp","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Notation.lean#L465-L465","name":"«term‹_›»","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/15895982054014726951.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Notation.html#«term‹_›»","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.c