l#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos","doc":"A byte position in a `String`. Internally, `String`s are UTF-8 encoded.\nCodepoint positions (counting the Unicode codepoints rather than bytes)\nare represented by plain `Nat`s instead.\nIndexing a `String` by a byte position is constant-time, while codepoint\npositions need to be translated internally to byte positions in linear-time. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1143-L1146","name":"Substring","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/1856444679572550697.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Prelude.html#Substring","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1148-L1149","name":"instInhabitedSubstring","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/83665610778764981.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Prelude.html#instInhabitedSubstring","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1151-L1152","name":"Substring.bsize","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/9866312628752097089.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Prelude.html#Substring.bsize","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1154-L1155","name":"String.csize","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/160338464425951597.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Prelude.html#String.csize","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1162-L1163","name":"String.utf8ByteSize","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/4101027821770969463.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/Prelude.html#String.utf8ByteSize","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1165-L1166","name":"String.bs