s its previous value. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L241-L245","name":"IO.iterate","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/16495787977783761209.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/System/IO.html#IO.iterate","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L261-L261","name":"IO.FS.Handle.mkPrim","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/8587970561014921759.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/System/IO.html#IO.FS.Handle.mkPrim","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L263-L264","name":"IO.FS.Handle.mk","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/9036379229458898443.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/System/IO.html#IO.FS.Handle.mk","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L271-L271","name":"IO.FS.Handle.isEof","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/9871839359406403661.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/System/IO.html#IO.FS.Handle.isEof","doc":"Returns whether the end of the file has been reached while reading a file.\n`h.isEof` returns true /after/ the first attempt at reading past the end of `h`.\nOnce `h.isEof` is true, reading `h` will always return an empty array.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L272-L272","name":"IO.FS.Handle.flush","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/16161394364224640941.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/System/IO.html#IO.FS.Handle.flush","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dca5da6b18d95ba75a16d5bcfb81fcb26705709a/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L273-L273","name":"IO.FS.Handle.read","link":"/LeanColls/docs/semantic/10287080083430462597.xml#","docLink":"/LeanColls/docs/Init/System/IO.html#IO.FS.Handle.read